description:
Celestial Masters is a collection of 72 animations generated from pixelart and psychedelic illustration.
Each animation also comes with a unique melody that corresponds to it.
This collection is the fruit of several months of effort. Apart from getting a unique piece of art, you get all the energy put into each of these NFTs, being part of our community.

Open your eyes and your heart, for the time of harvest has finally come.
Where will you be when the Master calls?
name: Celestial Masters (72)
